{"tid":675340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果6月4日WWDC 開發者大會即將登場，有哪些值得期待的？","createTime":"2018-05-23T12:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T13:14:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a4a3810166f2dd71f78fea51c6a231087a0d7d","tid":675340,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"陳伯安<br />\n<br />\nApple 於今日凌晨發布第 29 屆全球開發者大會（WWDC）的消息。日期將會從 6 月 4 號開始，舉辦為期四天。此次的舉辦地點位在美國加州的聖荷西。<br />\n<br />\n全球開發者大會，簡稱 WWDC（Worldwide Developers Conference），是一場為了全球開發者的年度大會。於為期四天的大會中包含演講、課程與研討會。WWDC 也利用此平台幫助參加者進行專業討論，一對一會談與意見、技術討論都包含在內。<br />\n<br />\n不過，最重要的是蘋果現任執行長提姆庫克（Tim Cook）的專題演講，其中將會揭露 Apple 認為 2018 年的科技潮流為何，還有即將推出的新產品與更新。這都是科技狂與蘋果迷們引頸期盼的大事。發表會的時間會在大會開始的第一天，現場也會進行直播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n這次發表會會推出的軟硬體設備都令人期待。其中包括下一代的 iOS 12、macOS、watchOS 還有 tvOS。而因為蘋果電腦的產品更新時間也快到了，iMac、MacBook、MacBook Pro、MacBook Air 的消息也可能會在發表會上出現。對於其他產品，包括延遲已久的 AirPower 無線充電板還有第二版的 AirPods 也是。另外，iPhone SE 2 、Apple Watch 3 都是可能會推出的產品名單之一。<br />\n<br />\nWWDC 的門票開賣時間在 3 月 22 日的早上十點開始（太平洋夏令時間），而門票要價 1,599 美元（大約臺幣 47,900 元）。"},{"pid":"efbe136e9a85948972372c2a8641f9f5f41f6339","tid":675340,"uid":3113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"冇新ipad pro <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6803300bdecc6f08d65412cbad8e59f7e5502f87","tid":675340,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"平反64？ 不了"},{"pid":"42d80d18f6afb3eea6f4d750cb7eacba0a6a848f","tid":675340,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"iTank, iTiananmen, iSquare, iXi, iCPC"},{"pid":"c5a161bc0417e88b187c337e743854e9cc5acfd2","tid":675340,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efbe136e9a85948972372c2a8641f9f5f41f6339","tid":675340,"uid":3113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"冇新ipad pro <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"iPad Mini <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00252d8471648866800938497337ae7612d48ae6","tid":675340,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"平板六四"},{"pid":"a9f0c9223c9152790ce3750c52d1cf434b94cf49","tid":675340,"uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"00252d8471648866800938497337ae7612d48ae6","tid":675340,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"平板六四"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20110308/large/08lp2p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20110308%2Flarge%2F08lp2p8.jpg&h=7d468278&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f5431a8cbaec558c5d1d9960541aab546dead1","tid":675340,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d473f4ecd745d0b9e786c965ab18ce731c5abdc","tid":675340,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"而門票要價 1,599 美元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40d8bd80f232760be92fa6267ddb3f1280e83d4","tid":675340,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d473f4ecd745d0b9e786c965ab18ce731c5abdc","tid":675340,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"而門票要價 1,599 美元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"好似有禮物拎走"